data.message: Design Workout: Glassmorphism card - final critique: Scores: 100% = 82%, 50% = 84%, 0% = 86%. Main gap: blob depth (~62%) - flat fills, no contrast zones. Key insight: glass isn't hero, background is. Fix: force top/bottom contrast, give blobs radial gradients, tint the glass. One compositional change = jump from low 80s to 90%+.
